description: Svetlana Tikhanovskaya, who says she won August's election, is wanted on an unspecified criminal charge.
title: Belarus: Russia puts opposition's Tikhanovskaya on wanted list
title_page: Belarus: Russia puts opposition's Tikhanovskaya on wanted list - BBC News
maintext: But Russia's Tass news agency reported that she was on the wanted list in Belarus and the Belarusian warrant against her would also be carried out in Russia according to agreements between the two countries.
